705506f-a.title: Brooklyn: Lorraine Street - Henry Street
705506f-a.text:
Lorraine Street, east from Henry Street to Hamilton Avenue,
showing in che foreground a recently constructed playground by the
City of New York. Beyond it is uhe Sapolin Co. located on Clinton
Street.
June 9, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
